<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-19780] Camel JBang does not support relative paths</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-19780</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When trying to execute a file through JBang, it doesn&apos;t recognize relative paths.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For instance, the following commands don&apos;t work:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
jbang -Dcamel.jbang.version=3.21.0 camel@apache/camel run ./&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;rest&lt;/span&gt;-dsl.camel.yaml

camel init /tmp/Test.java&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In contrast, the following works:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
jbang -Dcamel.jbang.version=3.21.0 camel@apache/camel run &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;rest&lt;/span&gt;-dsl.camel.yaml&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
